   CAREER BARRIERS ENCOUNTERED BY WOMEN (%)
 ----------------------------------------------
'Mens' club' network                     43
Prejudice of colleagues                  35
Lack of career guidance                  28
Sexual discrimination/harassment         23
Lack of training provision               18
Lack of personal motivation/confidence   18
Family commitments                       17
Inflexible working patterns              12
Social pressures (eg friends, parents)   12
Lack of adequate childcare                9
Insufficient education                    7
No barriers                              19
Other                                     9
