spot at Dollars 1,050 a tonne and shipment at Dollars 790-Dollars 800 a
tonne, cif. Nigerian ginger was offered at between Dollars 300 and Dollars
600 a tonne, ex-warehouse, depending on quality. Mexican pimento was quoted
at Dollars 1,700 a tonne, spot.
