present economic conditions. The operating loss of continuing business rose
partly because margins had suffered and costs had risen, and partly because
of the increased costs as the company explored various possibilities.
After a tax charge of Pounds 351,000 (Pounds 2,000) losses per share came to
1.4p (earnings 0.2p). The interim dividend is again 0.1p.
